|Entailment.Target entailment=the strength of social relations
|Entailment.Source inference=the strength of the fibers
}}{{Entailment
|Entailment.Target entailment=the strength/integrity of the social group as a whole depends on the strength/integrity of the relations between social members
|Entailment.Source inference=The strength/integrity of the textile as a whole is dependent on the strength/integrity of the individual fibers. 
}}{{Entailment
|Entailment.Target entailment=processes that affect the strength of the social group 
|Entailment.Source inference=processes that affect the strength of the fabric
